            <lg xml:id="TK435">
<l>varumuṉṉark kāvātāṉ vāḻkkai yerimuṉṉar</l>
<l>vaittūṟu pōlak keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The prosperity of him who does not timely guard against faults, will perish like straw before fire.</l>
